'''陆奥苹果'''1948年诞生在[[日本|日本]][[青森县|青森县]]，由金冠苹果和印度苹果杂交而成，其名字来自于青森县的旧称[[陆奥国|陆奥国]]。<ref>[http://www.orangepippin.com/apples/crispin.aspx Crispin apple] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090329023137/http://www.orangepippin.com/apples/crispin.aspx |date=2009-03-29 }}</ref>

'''陆奥苹果'''极易产生细菌性斑点（Pseudomonas syringae pv. papulans）。<ref name="disease"> [http://www.omafra.gov.on.ca/english/crops/hort/news/hortmatt/2005/12hrt05a5.htm Blister Spot on Mutsu (Crispin) Apples] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221022548/http://omafra.gov.on.ca/english/crops/hort/news/hortmatt/2005/12hrt05a5.htm |date=2009-02-21 }}, retrieved May 30, 2007</ref>

'''陆奥苹果'''2008年进入中国大陆市场，售价远高于一般民众能承受的水平。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dili.kantsuu.com/200912/20091211131318_167609.shtml|title=日本青森县的苹果，130年历史传奇|access-date=2012-03-16|archive-date=2017-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105081023/http://dili.kantsuu.com/200912/20091211131318_167609.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

